# GenAI Logistics â€“ Delivery Delay Prediction App

A Machine Learning based logistics project that predicts whether a shipment will be **delayed or delivered on time** based on:

- Distance (in km)  
- Traffic level (Low / Medium / High)  
- Weather conditions (Clear / Rain / Fog)

Built as an end-to-end project including:

1.Synthetic data generation  
2.ML model training (Random Forest)  
3.Streamlit web application  
4.Model deployment ready structure

---

## Demo Features

| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
|  ML Prediction | Predicts delivery delay using RandomForest |
|  Probability Score | Shows confidence % of delay |
|  Feature Importance | Shows which features influence prediction |
|  Streamlit UI | Simple web interface for users |
|  Encoded Inputs | Converts traffic + weather into model format |

---

