## How It Works (Pipeline)

1ï¸ Generate synthetic dataset  
 `python data_gen.py`

2ï¸ Train ML model  
 `python train_delay_model.py`  
Creates:  
 `delay_prediction_model.pkl`  
 `label_encoders.pkl`

3ï¸ Run Streamlit app  
 `streamlit run src/app.py`

4ï¸ Input fields appear â†’ choose Distance, Traffic, Weather â†’  
 Model predicts delay + probability

---

## Running Instructions

### Create Virtual Environment
    python -m venv .venv
    .venv\Scripts\activate (Windows)
### Install Dependencies
    pip install -r requirements.txt
### 3ï¸âƒ£ Generate Dataset
    python data_gen.py
### 4ï¸âƒ£ Train Model
    python train_delay_model.py
### 5ï¸âƒ£ Run Web App
    streamlit run src/app.py

